{"tid":2328504,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【ViuTV】《男排女將》We are the Littles (54) 黃金唔追返家瑜把撚呀！！！","createTime":"2020-12-16T14:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T14:47:30.000Z","uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ededec0663def3036362fa0ff5117664541d00","tid":2328504,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《男排女將》</span></strong><br />\n🏐<span class=\"gold\"><strong>We are the Littles</strong></span>🏐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/13aTarU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F13aTarU.jpg&h=5ff26785&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n\t</p><br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_GJkHeBw2uo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GJkHeBw2uo&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE19%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=8370ca3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_GJkHeBw2uo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cG-AHKwHMrk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcG-AHKwHMrk&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE19%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=56130916\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cG-AHKwHMrk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EcKNB5S2yzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEcKNB5S2yzI&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE19%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=c21a31db\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EcKNB5S2yzI</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LvGdZ1OnkdI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLvGdZ1OnkdI&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE19%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=a956e5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LvGdZ1OnkdI</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeY1ETH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeY1ETH.gif&h=de8178f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">全港首部男排港劇《男排女將》11月23號正式登場，<br />\n為大家送上一段香港排球運動員嘅奮鬥故事。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">故事講述，阿King（顧定軒飾）、Bobby（Anson Lo飾）、阿檸（Tiger飾）、方丈（Jer飾）、阿神（Edan飾）幾位熱愛排球的年輕人，原本是某甲一排球隊的成員，不過因為身高未達標準而遭人遺棄，他們對此憤憤不平，直至後來遇上蔣家瑜（鄧麗欣飾），幾位男生的命運從此改寫。<br />\n<br />\n蔣家瑜其實是前香港女子排球隊成員，因為幾年前一次沉重打擊，令她失去信心，過了好幾年渾渾噩噩的日子，當她遇上阿King這班人後，重燃鬥志，一發不可收拾，決定開創先河，成為全港首位擔任男子排球隊的女教練，球隊名為「力圖」，創團後隨即吸納新血，包括潛質優厚的魚仔（Ian飾）。<br />\n<br />\n「力圖」齊腳後，積極為參賽做準備，但家瑜堅持不做魔鬼教練，主張「開心排球」，但要求相當嚴謹，因為她認為這樣才能夠享受打排球的真正樂趣，一眾隊員在家瑜的帶領下，球技突飛猛進，與此同時，面對熱情投入的隊員，令家瑜決心改變，嘗試走出個人陰影，希望重新實現自己當職業排球員的夢想。<br />\n<br />\n當年被人笑謔的「矮仔」球隊，創造出一個又一個的「小傳奇」！他們用行動告訴大家「We are the Littles（我們不高）」，但別小看我們！</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">《男排女將》於2020年11月23日起逢星期一至五21:30－22:30於ViuTV播放。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6e5d026c6586661f2c7312f832ab1f82cda14b85","tid":2328504,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"小美仲推緊post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdf2d68ecdc603458b5fddd90db297dd5aeecfb","tid":2328504,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"【ViuTV】《男排女將》We are the Littles (54) 逃兵黃金嬲你啊！不想長大嗚嗚嗚嗚<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2328492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2328492</a><br />\n<br />\n大家請移玉步，撞post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f293b8d9aeb8d3c0ce687ecd699c4f0520bb07","tid":2328504,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"美人下次早啲"},{"pid":"fbaf7ccbd2e9d2b413e67cc9a238ba2fd9f6b8dd","tid":2328504,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47f293b8d9aeb8d3c0ce687ecd699c4f0520bb07","tid":2328504,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited